      <section id="id1165292335190">
        <title>Zigi helps Leo</title>
        <para id="id1165292335197">One day Zigi and Leo ran off to play in the forest.</para>
        <para id="id1165293851780">They rested in the shade of a tall tree.</para>
        <para id="id1165293851785">Sammy snake was naughty.</para>
        <para id="id1165293851789">He slithered down the tree to tease Zigi and Leo.</para>
        <para id="id1165293842829">Zigi did not hear Sammy Snake.</para>
        <para id="id1165293842833">Leo did not hear Sammy Snake.</para>
        <para id="id1165293820952">Sammy grabbed Leo.</para>
        <para id="id1165293820956">He curled his long body around Leo’s neck.</para>
        <para id="id1165293820961">He curled his long body around Leo’s body.</para>
        <para id="id1165292556517">He curled his long body around Leo’s legs.</para>
        <para id="id1165292556522">“Let go! Let go!” shouted Leo.</para>
        <para id="id1165293917602">“Let go! Let go!” shouted Zigi.</para>
        <para id="id1165292510732">But Sammy would not let go.</para>
        <list id="id1165292510736" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Tell the class what you think is going to happen. The title will help you.</item>
          <item>Discuss how you think a zebra can help a lion.</item>
          <item>If your friend were in trouble, would you help him/her?</item>
        </list>
